<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Resend OTP</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        /* Base Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #e4e8eb 100%);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        /* Container */
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        /* Header */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1e40af 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .logo span {
            color: #f97316;
        }
        
        h2 {
            color: white;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        
        /* Content */
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        
        .otp-container {
            background-color: #fff7ed;
            border: 2px dashed #fdba74;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
        }
        
        .expiry-note {
            color: #ea580c;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        /* Button */
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316 0%, #ea580c 100%);
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #64748b;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .social-icon {
            margin: 0 8px;
            color: #2563eb;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .company-info {
            margin-top: 15px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        /* Responsive */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                width: 100%;
                border-radius: 0;
                margin: 0;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 25px 15px;
            }
            
            .otp-code {
                font-size: 28px;
                padding: 10px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="padding: 20px;">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="logo">CRYSTAL<span>EVENTS</span></div>
                <h2>New Verification Code</h2>
            </div>
            
            <div class="content">
                <p>Hello, <%= name %>,</p>
                <p>We received a request for a new verification code for your Crystal Events account. Here's your new one-time password:</p>
                
                <div class="otp-container">
                    <div style="font-size: 15px; color: #4b5563;">Your new verification code</div>
                    <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
                    <div class="expiry-note">⚠️ Expires in 10 minutes</div>
                </div>
                
                <p style="margin-bottom: 25px;">For your security, this code will only be valid for a short time. If you didn't request this code, please secure your account by changing your password immediately.</p>
                
                <p>Need help? <a href="mailto:support@crystal-events.com" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">Contact our support team</a>.</p>
                
                <p>Best regards,<br><strong>The Crystal Events Team</strong></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer">
                <div class="social-links">
                    <a href="#" class="social-icon">Twitter</a> | 
                    <a href="#" class="social-icon">Facebook</a> | 
                    <a href="#" class="social-icon">Instagram</a>
                </div>
                <div class="company-info">
                    <p>© 2023 Crystal Event Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
                    <p>123 Event Plaza, Suite 500, San Francisco, CA 94107</p>
                    <p>Need help? Contact us at support@crystal-events.com</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>